data.description: The beautiful 4BR, 3 1/2 BA with spacious flex room is situated on premium lot in the wonderful community of Plantation at College Point.  As you approach the home you will be captivated by its pristine pavered and spacious driveway.  Upon entering the home you will take note of the boastful 9 foot ceilings, tray ceilings in living room, dining and master bedroom.  There is upgraded lighting throughout the home. EVP flooring in all areas except bedrooms, stainless steel appliances, and so much more.  The back patio is screened in overlooking the spacious fenced in back yard. There also is specific fenced area for dog run.  Call today to schedule a showing.*Buyer to verify anything deemed important*Washer & Dryer do not convey.
